resources.string:
To use the application create a blockchain-based Smart Asset following the steps here [link to instructions]

On the stage of Smart Asset validation:

1) Launch application;

2) Scan the QR code of the Asset that needs to be validated;

3) On the main page of the application, press the “Shake” button or simply shake your phone to generate a motion sensor signal;

4) On the main page of the application press the “Photo” button to generate a geolocation sensor signal and photo-verification;

5) Check for validation confirmation on the Smart Asset page.

